name: OtherDiabetes
title: Other Diabetes
purpose: (Clinical Focus: The purpose of this value set is to represent concepts for a diagnosis of  diabetes.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use a model element related to Diagnosis.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes concepts that represent a diagnosis of diabetes where the code is not specific to type I or type II.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes concepts that represent a diagnosis of gestational diabetes or steroid-induced diabetes.)
